@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #ECF0F1
  BorderColor #2C3E50
  FontColor #1B2631
  ArrowColor #2C3E50
}

title Variant lifecycle — state diagram

[*] --> Raw

Raw : entered as chr:pos:ref:alt
Raw --> Canonicalized : parse + normalize

Canonicalized : variant_key = "17:44075760:G:A"
Canonicalized --> Featurized : cache lookup (dbNSFP)
Canonicalized --> VEPFetched : cache miss

VEPFetched : Ensembl VEP REST (GRCh38)
VEPFetched --> Featurized : + AA chemistry computed locally

Featurized : 39-column vector + imputation flags
Featurized --> Scored : XGBoost predict_proba

Scored : p_raw in [0,1]
Scored --> Calibrated : isotonic transform

Calibrated : p_calibrated + 95% CI
Calibrated --> Explained : TreeSHAP per-feature

Explained : top-15 SHAP values
Explained --> Reported : render UI / JSON

Reported --> [*]

note right of Raw
  Rejected if parse fails
  or non-missense (len(ref) != 1
  or len(alt) != 1)
end note

note right of VEPFetched
  Rejected if no missense
  consequence on canonical
  transcript
end note

note right of Reported
  Risk bands:
    p ≥ 0.75 → pathogenic
    0.25 < p < 0.75 → uncertain
    p ≤ 0.25 → benign
end note

@enduml
